<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Password Reset Request</title>
  <style>
      body {
        width: 100% !important;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Noto Sans", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif !important;
        background-color: #0f0e10;
        color: #e8f6fe !important;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }
      h1,
      h2,
      h3 {
        text-transform: uppercase !important;
        letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
        font-weight: 500 !important;
        font-family: "Squada One", "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      p,
      span, li {
        color: #e8f6fe !important;
      }
      a {
        color: #34aaf3 !important;
        font-weight: 500 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: all 0.3s ease-out;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #e4457b !important;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      a:visited {
        color: #fcb614 !important;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #19181a !important;
        padding: 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0;
      }
      .header img {
        max-width: 100px;
        height: auto;
      }
      .main-content {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .main-content h3 {
        color: #34aaf3 !important;
        font-size: 32px !important;
      }
      .main-content p {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        line-height: 1.5 !important;
      }
      li {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        line-height: 1.5 !important;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 25px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #34aaf3;
        color: #000000 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        border-radius: 999px !important;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #e4457b;
        color: #fceaf0;
      }
      blockquote {
        display: block;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: rgba(100, 109, 114, 0.1);
        color: #e2e6ea !important;
        border-radius: 999px !important;
        margin: 20px 0;
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 4px !important;
        background-color: #0f0e10;
      }
      .footer a {
        color: #34aaf3 !important;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer a:hover {
        color: #e4457b !important;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer a:visited {
        color: #ffb300 !important;
      }
      .social-icons {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .social-icons img {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }
      .bbm-team {
        color: #e1306c !important; 
        font-weight: 600 !important;
      }
      .sign {
        font-family: "Playwrite MX", cursive !important;
      }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
        body {
          background-color: #fff !important;
          color: #062030 !important;
        }
        p,
        span, li {
          color: #062030 !important;
        }
        .container {
          background-color: rgba(241, 250, 254, 1) !important;
        }
        .main-content h3 {
          color: #007bff !important;
        }
        .btn {
          background-color: #007bff !important;
          color: #ffffff !important;
        }
        .btn:hover {
          color: #fceaf0 !important;
          background-color: #e1306c !important;
          text-decoration: none !important;
        }
        blockquote {
          background-color: rgba(29, 161, 242, 0.1) !important;
          color: #062030 !important;
        }
        a {
          color: #007bff !important;
        }
        a:hover {
          color: #e1306c !important;
          text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer {
          background-color: rgba(29, 161, 242, 0.1) !important;
        }
        .footer a {
          color: #007bff !important;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
          color: #e1306c !important;
          text-decoration: underline;
        }
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Password Reset Request</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{username}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email.</p>
      <p>To reset your password, please click the button below:</p>
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      </p>
      <p>If the button above does not work, please copy and paste the following URL into your web browser:</p>
      <p><a href="{{resetLink}}">{{resetLink}}</a></p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>The BullBearMastery Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at support@bullbearmastery.com.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
